snippet.title: tERRORbane -  A̶n̶i̶m̶a̶t̶e̶d̶ Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist tERRORbane on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/16...

tERRORbane is a comedic adventure where bugs are your FRIENDS! Enjoy exploring a crazy and outlandish world, full of unique, quirky characters and homages to the history of videogaming, challenge the Developer with your creativity and be the Bane of Errors!

Follow the game on:
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/Terrorbane_BNS
Facebook: https://www.fb.com/Terrorbane
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/terrorbane
Discord: https://discord.gg/AyAvVbcHua
